This paper deals with visual recognition tasks and deep neural networks, which are commonly studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The paper also discusses bias and fairness, which are topics of interest in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper uses datasets of images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
